                <head>No. 666<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On February 17 and 18 Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_DJF1"
                        >Dulles</persName> discussed the Saar with <persName corresp="#p_BGP1"
                        >Bidault</persName> at Berlin and with <persName corresp="#p_AK1"
                        >Adenauer</persName> at Wahn Airport. For records of these conversations,
                    see the memorandum by the Secretary of State, <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v07p1#d497">Document 497</ref>, and the memorandum of
                    conversation by <persName corresp="#p_MDII1">MacArthur</persName>, <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v07p1#d527">Document 527</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
